displayChart.description: Your weekly update of the most popular tracks in Chandigarh, India.

labels.name: Sony Music Entertainment India Pvt. Ltd.

highlights.text: Sidhu Moose Wala has the most spots on Top Songs Chandigarh. Never Fold is the highest at #15.
Schedule by Tegi Pannu and Manni Sandhu has been on Top Songs Chandigarh the longest, at 68 weeks straight.
SPAIN by Jassa Dhillon and thiarajxtt is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Chandigarh, up 44 spots at #13.
Hood Famous by Navaan Sandhu is the highest new entry on Top Songs Chandigarh at #11.
